All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    An interface for the representation and for solving of Sudokus, which provides all methods for editing.
    EnforceCell
    Solution strategy, that checks for all non-fix cells, if there is only one possibility left.
    EnforceNumber
    Solution strategy, that checks for all non-fix cells, if it's possible, based on the possibilities for that cell, to find an enforced number.
    FirstSolutionThread
    Thread to calculate first solution for given board.
    InvalidSudokuException
    Exception if one likes to set a number which is not possible.
    Saturator
    An interface which must be implemented by classes which provide a solution strategy for a Sudoku puzzle.
    Structure
    The different types of structures/coordinate systems.
    SudokuBoard
    Board model for sudoku game with nxm inner boxes, n=length of inner box-row and m=length of inner box-col.
    SudokuBoardSolver
    Sudoku board solver, to solve a sudoku-board with strategies and guess-algorithms and find all possible solutions to it.
    SudokuController
    Controller class for Sudoku-GUI application.
    SudokuFile
    Sudoku file class, to parse file to model.
    SudokuFrame
    Frame class, renders content to display.
    SudokuMain
    Main class for Sudoku-GUI application.
    SudokuModel
    Model class, holds information about game-board.
    SudokuObservable
    This class represents an observable model object.
    SudokuObserver
    Sudoku observer class, gets informed about changes in model.
    SudokuSolver
    An interface for solving Sudoku puzzles.
    SudokuView
    View class, represents the game-board of the model and can be used as an interface for the user to make an input.
    ThreadObservable
    This class represents an observable thread object.
    ThreadObserver
    Thread observer class, gets informed about changes in observable objects.
    UnsolvableSudokuException
    Exception if board gets unsolvable.
